Package edu.citadel.cprl.ast

Class UnaryExpr

java.lang.Object
edu.citadel.cprl.ast.AST
edu.citadel.cprl.ast.Expression
edu.citadel.cprl.ast.UnaryExpr
Direct Known Subclasses:
NegationExpr, NotExpr
public abstract class UnaryExpr
extends Expression
Base class for all unary expressions. A unary expression is an expression of the form "operator expression". The expression following the operator is called the operand. A simple example would be "-x".
